Name: Scalegorge Tidalflow (I)
Desc: Enemies have Exo-Toughness and their actions are delayed by <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#2[i]%</unbreak></color> after they are Weakness Broken. At the same time, add <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak></color> hit(s) to "Memory Turbulence"'s Hits Per Action. If the target is an Elite enemy or higher, then additionally add <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#8[i]</unbreak></color> hit(s), up to a max of <color=#f29e38ff><unbreak>#5[i]</unbreak></color> hits.\nAt the start of every Cycle, every hit by the "Memory Turbulence" causes 1 instance of DMG, dealing a set amount of DMG to random enemy targets.

Challenge.Name: Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Win with at least <unbreak>#1[i]</unbreak> Cycle(s) left
Have no downed characters
